Tom Lenk https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Lenk 0 Thomas Loren Lenk (born June 16, 1976) is an American stage and television actor best known for starring as Andrew Wells in the television series Buffy the Vampire Slayer and its spin-off Angel.
